title: Coronavirus: Italy Total Death Toll Rises 11 Percent in 24 Hours, Exceeds 6,000
description: In the last 24 hours, 602 people have died in Italy from the Chinese coronavirus, bringing the nation's total death toll from the virus to 6,078 on Monday, up from 5,476 on Sunday -- an increase of 11 percent in one day.
content:
